                    <h3 id="create-user">Create user</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Call: POST <code>apps/{appId}/users</code></li>
                        <li>Registers a new user</li>
                        <li>App Authentication is required if it is set in the configuration file</li>
                        <li>User ID and User e-mail cannot be taken</li>
                    </ul>
